.TH "doc_write_data_area" 9 "doc_write_data_area" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
doc_write_data_area \- Write data into data area
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" doc_write_data_area
.BI "(struct docg3 *docg3 "  ","
.BI "const void *buf "  ","
.BI "int len "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "docg3" 12
the device
.IP "buf" 12
the buffer to get input bytes from
.IP "len" 12
the length to write
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Writes bytes into flash data. Handles the single byte / even bytes writes.
